{
  "stem": "21310.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this-- what I remember of that winter, it was a very, very severe winter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The schools were closed and not only for-- like, the high schools were all closed, and not only for Jewish kids but all the Gentile kids.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The high schools were closed, but the vocational schools were open because they-- I guess the Germans needed the-- the people who are trades people or people who could work with their hands.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but-- and elementary schools were open, but I understand that there was no-- they didn't teach geography or history in the elementary school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also in the beginning, they immediately arrested the Polish intelligentsia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, that was Jews and non-Jews alike-- I mean, teachers, lawyers, doctors, priests, anybody who could be in a leadership position and organize some resistance.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- well, some people, I guess, were sent away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I understand that over 2,000 were shot in the environment of Warsaw in the forest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot the name of the forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because people were talking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we weren't in the ghetto so people were talking about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was known.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- because they would come to an apartment, take the people or take these men out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they even called this area 'a circle of death' because it was surrounded Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were over 2,000 people that were shot in this in 1939.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were all from the higher echelon in society.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed in this apartment [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in-- in the winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, it was-- it was in the fall, the maid got typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was like dysentery, you know, like salmonella or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
